<p>
<strong>Translated</strong> and <strong>Memopal</strong> team up to offer a unique opportunity to the smartest, most creative and innovative web designer. By joining our team you will work on a range of tasks that will challenge your creative side and push you to develop original solutions to guarantee the best communication and user experience for our customers, vendors and software users.</p>
